stand how visitors interact with our site to improve performance and content.</li>\r\n            <li><strong>Functional Cookies:</strong> Enable enhanced functionality and personalization, like language or region preferences.</li>\r\n            <li><strong>Advertising & Targeting Cookies:</strong> Used to deliver relevant ads based on your interests.</li>\r\n            <li><strong>Social Media Cookies:</strong> Enable social sharing features directly from our site.</li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"section\">\r\n        <h2>Third-Party Cookies</h2>\r\n        <p>We may partner with trusted third parties who place cookies on your device to support analytics or advertising services. These cookies are controlled by the third party, and we do not have direct control over them.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"section\">\r\n        <h2>Your Choices Regarding Cookies</h2>\r\n        <p>You can choose how cookies are managed on your device:</p>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li>Adjust your browser settings to block or delete cookies.</li>\r\n            <li>Use browser tools or extensions to manage cookie preferences.</li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <p>Note: Blocking or disabling cookies may affect website functionality or prevent certain features from working.</p>\r\n        <p>Browser guides:</p>\r\n        <ul>\r\n            <li><a href=\"https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647?hl=en&co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop\" target=\"_blank\">Cookie settings in Google Chrome</a></li>\r\n            <li><a href=\"https://www.firefox.com/en-US/privacy/websites/cookie-settings/\" target=\"_blank\">Cookie settings in Mozilla Firefox</a></li>\r\n            <li><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-lk/guide/safari/ibrw850f6c51/mac\" target=\"_blank\">Cookie settings in Safari</a></li>\r\n            <li><a href=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/manage-cookies-in-microsoft-edge-view-allow-block-delete-and-use-168dab11-0753-043d