<+><!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\">\r\n\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <title>Vendora | Terms & Conditions</title>\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css/base.css\">\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css/components.css\">\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css/footer.css\">\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css/layout.css\">\r\n\r\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Condensed&family=Playfair+Display&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css\">\r\n</head>\r\n\r\n<body class=\"home-bg\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"service-card\">\r\n    <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>\r\n    <p>These Terms and Conditions govern your use of the Vendora platform. By accessing or using our website, you agree to be bound by these terms.</p>\r\n\r\n    <h3>Definition</h3>\r\n    <p>For the purposes of these Terms and Conditions, the following terms shall have the meanings set out below:</p>\r\n\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li><strong>“Vendora”</strong> refers to the online beauty store platform operated under the name Vendora, including its website, services, and related systems.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>“User”</strong> refers to any individual or entity accessing or using the platform, including customers, suppliers, and delivery personnel.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>“Customer”</strong> refers to a user who purchases products through the platform.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>“Supplier”</strong> refers to a user who lists, manages, or provides products available for sale on the platform.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>“Delivery Personnel”</strong> refers to individuals responsible for delivering orders to customers.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>“Account”</strong> refers to the registered profile created by a user to access platform services.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>“Order”</strong> refers to a request placed by a customer to purchase one or more products through the platform.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>“Services”</strong> refers to all functionalities provided by Vendora, including browsing, ordering, payment processing, and delivery coordination.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n\r\n    <h3>Account Registration</h3>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>Users must provide accurate and complete information during registration.</li>\r\n        <li>Users are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of their login credentials.</li>\r\n        <li>Any activity performed under your account is your responsibility.</li>\r\n        <li>Users may delete their accounts at any time through the system.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n\r\n    <h3>Use of the Platform</h3>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>The platform must be used only for lawful purposes.</li>\r\n        <li>Users must not misuse, disrupt, or attempt unauthorized access to the system.</li>\r\n        <li>Vendora reserves the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n\r\n    <h3>Products & Services</h3>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>Vendora provides beauty products including cosmetics, skincare, haircare, body care, fragrances, and beauty tools.</li>\r\n        <li>We strive to ensure that product descriptions and images are accurate, but minor variations may occur.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n\r\n    <h3>Orders & Payments</h3>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>Orders can be placed through the website by registered users.</li>\r\n        <li>We support both secure online payments and cash on delivery.</li>\r\n        <li>All payments are processed through secure systems.</li>\r\n        <li>Orders may be cancelled within 24 hours of placement.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n\r\n    <h3>Delivery Policy</h3>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>Orders are delivered within 3–5 business days.</li>\r\n        <li>Users must provide accurate delivery information.</li>\r\n        <li>If incorrect delivery details are provided, delivery will be attempted us