y result in account suspension or removal from the platform.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<footer class=\"footer\">\r\n    <div class=\"footer-bottom\">\r\n        <p>© 2026 Vendora | The Online Beauty Store</p>\r\n        <p><button><a href=\"terms.html\">Terms & Conditions</a></button> | <button><a href=\"privacy.html\">Privacy Policy</a></button> | <button><a href=\"cookie.html\">Cookie Policy</a></button> | Do Not Sell My Personal Information | Vendora</p>\r\n        <p>If you are having problems using this website, please <button><a href=\"service.html\">CLICK HERE</a></button> for assistance.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</footer>\r\n<script src=\"../js/main.js\"></script>\r\n<script src=\"../js/policy.js\"></script>\r\n<script src=\"../js/service.js\"></script>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n
