+</head>
+
+<body class="home-bg">
+<div class="service-card">
+    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
+
+    <p><strong>1. Do I need an account to place an order?</strong><br>
+        Yes, you need to create an account to place orders and track your purchases.</p>
+
+    <p><strong>2. How do I place an order?</strong><br>
+        Browse products, add your desired items to the cart, and proceed to checkout to complete your
+        purchase.</p>
+
+    <p><strong>3. What payment methods are available?</strong><br>
+        We accept Credit/Debit Cards and Cash on Delivery (COD) for your convenience.</p>
+
+    <p><strong>4. How can I track my order?</strong><br>
+        You can track your order through the "Track Orders" section in your account after logging in.
+    </p>
+
+    <p><strong>5. Can I cancel or modify my order?</strong><br>
+        Yes, you can cancel or modify your order before it has been shipped.</p>
+
+    <p><strong>6. How long does delivery take?</strong><br>
+        Delivery usually takes between 3–5 working days depending on your location.</p>
+
+    <p><strong>7. What should I do if I receive a damaged or wrong product?</strong><br>
+        Please contact our support team immediately to request a replacement or refund.</p>
+
+    <p><strong>8. Are the products authentic?</strong><br>
+        Yes, all products sold on Vendora are 100% genuine and sourced from trusted suppliers.</p>
+
+    <p><strong>9. Can I return a product?</strong><br>
+        Yes, returns are accepted within a limited time period if the product meets our return policy
+        conditions.</p>
+
+    <p><strong>10. How can I contact customer support?</strong><br>
+        You can contact us via the contact form or email at the bottom of this page</p>
+</div>
